flowchart TD
    DEV[Developer pushes code] --> GH[GitHub]

    GH --> PR{Pull Request?}

    PR -->|Yes| PR_VAL[PR Validation workflow]
    PR_VAL --> TITLE[Check PR title\nConventional Commits]
    PR_VAL --> LABEL[Auto-label PR]
    PR_VAL --> SIZE[Check PR size]

    PR -->|Yes / Push to main| CI[CI workflow]
    CI --> TC[Type Check\npnpm lint]
    CI --> TEST[Unit Tests\npnpm test:unit]
    CI --> BUILD[Build\npnpm build]
    CI --> OPENAPI[OpenAPI drift check\non PRs only]

    PR -->|Yes / Push to main| CODEQL[CodeQL Security Analysis]
    PR -->|Yes| DEPREVIEW[Dependency Review\nfail on HIGH severity]

    GH -->|Push to main| MIGRATE{supabase/migrations\nchanged?}
    MIGRATE -->|Yes| SUPABASE[Supabase Deploy\ndb push to production]
    SUPABASE --> ENV{production env\napproval required}

    GH -->|Schedule Mon 6AM| CODEQL_SCHED[Weekly CodeQL Scan]

    GH -->|Schedule Mon 6AM| DEPENDABOT[Dependabot\ndependency updates]

    CI -->|All pass| VERCEL[Vercel auto-deploy\npreview / production]
